ait. I am a hospitality major and am going to graduate school for hospitality administration at UNLV and I can say that Caesars truly practices what my professors preach when it comes to customer service. I had a great trip and my only complaint is that I didnt sleep in my amazing bed more than 5 hours in the 5 days I was there. I cannot wait for my next trip to Caesars.	
